OL,6,FBritish dog owners and walkers have
OL,7,Fbeen warned of a "flesh-eating"
OL,8,Fdisease affecting pets, with new cases
OL,9,Fconfirmed across the UK.
OL,11,FA number of cases have been reported
OL,12,Fthis year in Wales, Scotland and the
OL,13,FNorth of England.
OL,15,FIt's particularly prevalent at this
OL,16,Ftime of year when the ground is soggy
OL,17,Fdue to increased rainfall.
OL,19,FHere's what to watch out for, to stop
OL,20,Fthe deadly disorder developing on your
OL,21,Ffour-legged friend.
