OL,6,FWhat is Alabama rot?
OL,8,FAlabama rot, otherwise known as
OL,9,FCutaneous and Renal Glomerular
OL,10,FVasculopathy (CRGV), is a disease that
OL,11,Faffects dogs.
OL,13,FIt damages the blood vessels in the
OL,14,Fskin and kidneys, which causes visible
OL,15,Fsores on the skin and can lead to
OL,16,Fsevere organ dysfunction and
OL,17,Fultimately kidney failure.
OL,19,FThe cause of the disease is currently
OL,20,Funknown, though research is ongoing.
