OL,3,C'Surge' in Alabama rot: How to spot
OL,4,Cthe deadly dog disease
OL,6,FAlabama rot was first identified in
OL,7,Fgreyhounds in the United States in the
OL,8,F1980s but there have been reports of
OL,9,Fthe disease across the UK.
OL,11,FIn 2012, just six cases were reported
OL,12,Fin the UK, but this number has
OL,13,Fcontinued to rise each year since.
OL,15,FMost reports come from pet owners who
OL,16,Fwalk their dogs in the countryside,
OL,17,Fand most cases are reported during
OL,18,Fwinter and spring.
